Node "Lacey03_bFEM"
notes "Branch 3 is where Lacey can talk a bit about herself."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "A gal who fancies the sweeter sex, hmm? Don't worry honey. You're not the first. Price-wise, it depends on the girl. Have you seen one who takes your fancy?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "There aren't any girls up here, but I've seen plenty of ghouls." linkto "Lacey03_c1_MID_CHR" conditions { CHECK_STAT charisma <= 7 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "There aren't any girls up here, but I've seen plenty of ghouls." linkto "Lacey03_c1_HIGH_CHR" conditions { CHECK_STAT strength > 7 link_next NONE } notes ""
