Node "Lacey05"
notes "Branch 5 is where the PC can find out about Lacey's plans to sell extremely valuable Vault-Tec pillow-talk secrets to the Chinese."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "It started out innocent enough. Well, innocent for us. One of the girls I was responsible for got roughed up by one of our \"clients\"."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_02a"  notes ""
