Node "Lacey05_07a"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "By the time Willow 'n' me are done wringing him dry, we got enough money to make sure the girl who got hurt don't have to worry about cash for the rest of her days. There's even enough left over for me and Willow to get a taste of the action, too."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_08a"  notes ""
