              }
}
Node "Lacey05_08a"
notes "Branch 5 is where the PC can find out about Lacey's plans to sell extremely valuable Vault-Tec pillow-talk secrets to the Chinese."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Then I start thinking bigger. When you screw a man in my line of work, he can leave himself open in a couple of ways. He can get you to do nasty shit he'd never tell anyone else about, or he opens up and starts talking, once the deed is done. Maybe both."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_09a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Is this \"screw\" as in con or have sex?" linkto "Lacey05_09b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just skip to the end and tell me what the machine does." linkto "Lacey05_tldr"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_08b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Enough for the two of us to see the nicer side of life for a couple of months before having to come back to... well... this."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_08a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_09a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Willow and me, we get more daring. Pretty soon, we're blackmailing all sorts of greaseballs. The money's good. One day, we get a Vault-Tec exec who likes to do bathroom stuff whilst he's doing bedroom stuff, if you catch my drift."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_10a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't catch your drift." linkto "Lacey05_10b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just skip to the end and tell me what the machine does." linkto "Lacey05_tldr"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_09b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[She gives you a look that can only be described as \"ripe\"]. Sex, honey. I'm talking about sex."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_09a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_10a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "We press him for cash. He buckles, but offers something juicier: dirt on people at the very top of the company."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_11a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The CEO, you mean?" linkto "Lacey05_11b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just skip to the end and tell me what the machine does." linkto "Lacey05_tldr"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_10b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "You don't... If I use the term \"golden shower\" does that... uh... make it any clearer?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Stare blankly at her]" linkto "Lacey05_11a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Gross. I wish I hadn't asked." linkto "Lacey05_11a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_11a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Turns out he's as good as his word. He delivers a holo with details of contract fraud, money laundering, hell, even experiments on human subjects, if you can believe that."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_12a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tests on human subjects?" linkto "Lacey05_12b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just skip to the end and tell me what the machine does." linkto "Lacey05_tldr"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_11b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "That like the chief exec? Yup. The stink follows all the way to the top."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_11a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_12a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "It's gold dust. Toilet boy tells us the Chinese would pay out-of-this world bucks for a scoop like this and tells us how to get in touch with them. Turns out he was thinking of turning stool pigeon himself. Too bad he had to sell us his golden egg."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_13a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're prepared to sell out your own country?" linkto "Lacey05_13b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_12b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yeah, crazy stuff, like out of a comic. They even had plans to do experiments on people in those fallout shelters they're building."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Lacey05_12a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lacey05_13a"
notes "A variable needs to mark that the conversation in branch Lacey05 has been completed."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The machine you found? It's tuned into a numbers machine, or somesuch. When the time comes, a message'll come through, telling us when and where to meet their people. When that day comes, I'll be the richest woman in town."
      options {
              }
}
